	<h1 class="title">上海这场没有真迹的梵高展，为什么会有人买单？</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/99238/small/99238.jpg?1435570983" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">孙今泾 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-05-21 09:20:00 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/9836/medium/9836.jpg?1436654781" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="9836" data-title="《上海这场没有真迹的梵高展，为什么会有人买单？》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/9836/medium/9836.jpg?1436654781" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/9836.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
